        <abstract> 
<p>Thinks FD should review Julius von Wiesner’s book [<hi rend="italic">Das Bewegungsvermögen der Pflanzen</hi> (1881)]. CD comforted that Wiesner’s experiments support their findings but finds it laughable how differently he has interpreted them.</p> 
